  <brief_title>Preoperative Catastrophizing Predicts Pain Outcome After Shoulder, Knee and Hip Arthroplasty</brief_title>
  <official_title>Preoperative Catastrophizing Predicts Pain Outcome After Shoulder, Knee and Hip Arthroplasty</official_title>
